lume\">Vol:</label>&nbsp;</font></th>\n                          <td><input type=\"text\" name=\"volume\" id=\"qsintdefsvolume\" size=\"4\" maxlength=\"10\" value=\"\" style=\"font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica;font-size:10px;\"></td>\n                          <th><font size=\"-2\" face=\"verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif\" color=\"#000000\"><label for=\"qsintdefsfirstpage\">Page:</label>&nbsp;</font></th>\n                          <td><input type=\"text\" name=\"firstpage\" id=\"qsintdefsfirstpage\" size=\"4\" maxlength=\"10\" value=\"\" style=\"font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica;font-size:10px;\"></td>\n                        </tr>\n                      </tbody></table>\n                    </td>\n                    <td bgcolor=\"#DBDBDB\"><img alt=\" \" width=\"2\" height=\"2\" src=\"/icons/spacer.gif\"></td>\n                  </tr>\n                </tbody></table>\n              </form>\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody></table>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td colspan=\"3\">\n        <img alt=\" \" width=\"2\" height=\"2\" src=\"/icons/spacer.gif\"><br>\n        <hr align=\"left\" size=\"1\" color=\"#000000\" noshade=\"\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody></table>\n  <h2><font color=\"#006633\" face=\"Trebuchet MS\">About Journal of General Virology</font></h2>\n  <h3>ISSNs: Print 0022-1317;&nbsp;Online 1465-2099</h3>\n  <hr>\n  <p><font face=\"Trebuchet MS\"><b>Journal of General Virology</b></font></p>\n  <p>JGV, a dynamic journal at the forefront of virology today, attracts an international audience and publishes over 3500 pages of rigorously peer-reviewed, high-calibre research from around the world.</p>\n  <p>The diverse scope of the journal, which reflects the evolving nature of virology today, includes topics on all aspects of animal, plant, insect, bacterial and fungal viruses, transmissible spongiform encephalopathies, molecular biology and immunology, virushost interactions and antiviral compounds.</p>\n  <hr>\n  <p><font color=\"#006633\" face=\"Trebuchet MS\"><b>JGV Online features:</b></font></p>\n  <ul>\n    <li>\n      <a href=\"/vir/misc/direct.shtml\">JGV Direct</a> - free access to selected papers up to 3 months ahead of print\n    </li>\n    <li>Sophisticated search tools</li>\n    <li>Inter-article and cross-journal linking</li>\n    <li>Supplementary data facility</li>\n    <li>Links to Medline and GenBank</li>\n    <li>Citation tracking and alerts</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p><font color=\"#006633\" face=\"Trebuchet MS\"><b>Benefits to authors:</b></font></p>\n  <ul>\n    <li>Expert and rigorous review process</li>\n    <li>Excellent editorial standards</li>\n    <li>Online submission and peer review</li>\n    <li>Publish ahead of print scheme</li>\n    <li>Supplementary data facility</li>\n    <li>No page charges</li>\n    <li>Free colour reproduction</li>\n    <li>25 free offprints</li>\n  </ul>\n  <ul>\n    <li>\n      <a href=\"/vir/misc/self_archiving.dtl\">Self-archiving</a>. Details of the SGM policy on author self-archiving\n    </li>\n    <li>\n      <a href=\"/vir/misc/open_option.dtl\">Paid immediate open access</a>. Details of the SGM Open Option scheme that allows immediate open access to articles\n    </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p><font color=\"#006633\" face=\"Trebuchet MS\"><b>Impact factor:</b></font></p>\n  <ul>\n    <li><i>Journal of General Virology</i>'s impact factor for 2007 is 3.120</li>\n  </ul>\n  <hr>\n  <h3><a name=\"EO\" id=\"EO\"></a><b>Editorial Office</b></h3>\n  <p>Permission requests should be sent to <span id=\"em0\">m.asbury{at}sgm.ac.uk</span>\n   (Editorial Assistant) at the Editorial Office.</p>\n  <p>All other queries should be directed to <span id=\"em1\">n.wilder{at}sgm.ac.uk</span>\n   (Senior Staff Editor) at the Editorial Office.<br></p>\n  <p>JGV Editorial Office<br>\n  Society for General Microbiology<br>\n  Marlborough House<br>\n  Basingstoke Road<br>\n  Spencers Wood<br>\n  Reading RG7 1AG<br>\n  UK</p><b>E-mail:</b> <span id=\"em2\">jgv{at}sgm.ac.uk</span>\n  <br>\n  <b>Tel:</b> +44 (0)118 988 1833<br>\n  <b>Fax:</b> +44 (0)118 988 1834<br>\n  <hr>\n  <p>Last modified 1 September 2008</p>\n  <p></p>\n  <hr noshade=\"\" align=\"left\" width=\"450\">\n  <table cellpadding=\"2\" cellspacing=\"2\" width=\"450\">\n    <tbody><tr>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#007E18\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/vir/\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">HOME</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#007E18\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/vir/help/\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">HELP</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#007E18\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/vir/cgi/feedback\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">FEEDBACK</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#007E18\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/vir/subscriptions\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">SUBSCRIPTIONS</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#007E18\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/vir/contents-by-date.0.shtml\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">ARCHIVE</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#007E18\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/vir/search.dtl\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">SEARCH</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td width=\"75\" nowrap=\"\"></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody></table>\n  <table cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"2\" width=\"375\">\n    <tbody><tr>\n      <td alig